es_004.jpg\"><img alt=\"hungergames_004.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2012/09/hungergames_004-thumb-450x298-1925.jpg\" width=\"450\" class=\"mt-image-center\" style=\"text-align: center; display: block; margin: 0 auto 20px;\"></a></div><div><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2012/09/21/hungergames_002.jpg\"><img alt=\"hungergames_002.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2012/09/hungergames_002-thumb-450x298-1927.jpg\" width=\"450\" class=\"mt-image-center\" style=\"text-align: center; display: block; margin: 0 auto 20px;\"></a></div><div><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2012/09/21/hungergames_005.jpg\"><img alt=\"hungergames_005.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2012/09/hungergames_005-thumb-450x298-1929.jpg\" width=\"450\" class=\"mt-image-center\" style=\"text-align: center; display: block; margin: 0 auto 20px;\"></a></div> \t\t</div>","date":1348196700000,"haveTrans":true,"id":7280,"pic":"https://ikuta.club/nogizaka/blog/20120921/7280_0.jpg","title":"「ハンガー・ゲーム」プレミアム試写会に参加しました。","transContent":"<div class=\"entrybodyin\">\n\t\t<div><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2012/09/21/hungergames_000.jpg\"><img alt=\"hungergames_000.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2012/09/hungergames_000-thumb-450x298-1919.jpg\" width=\"450\" class=\"mt-image-center\" style=\"text-align: center; display: block; margin: 0 auto 20px;\"></a></div><div><br></div><div>9月20日，生田绘梨花，生驹里奈，樱井玲香出席了在东京都内举办的汉格游戏的日本首映式。</div><div><br></div><div>与电影的主题相结合，作为“战斗女主角”，伦敦奥运会银牌</div><div>INACE神户莱奥萨的大野忍选手和近贺有缘选手也登上了舞台。</div><div><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2012/09/21/hungergames_003.jpg\"><img alt=\"hungergames_003.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2012/09/hungergames_003-thumb-450x298-1921.jpg\" width=\"450\" class=\"mt-image-center\" style=\"text-align: center; display: block; margin: 0 auto 20px;\"></a></div><div><br></div><div>事先在本作品的日语版配音声优的宝座上，举办了“声优夏日甄选”。因此，生田绘梨花获得了女主角的对手“少女鲁”角色的宝座。在舞台上说：“虽然很紧张，但是能给我这样一个重要的角色，我很高兴。”评论了。</div><div><br></div><div><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2012/09/21/hungergames_001.jpg\"><img alt=\"hungergames_001.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2012/09/hungergames_001-thumb-450x298-1923.jpg\" width=\"450\" class=\"mt-image-center\" style=\"text-align: center; display: block; margin: 0 auto 20px;\"></a></div><div><br></div><div>另外，生驹里奈让我碰上了大野选手的银牌，“有一瞬间，我感到非常的沉重，很紧张”的表情一边开心地评论着。更进一步说，“最近，像电影一样生存的经验是什么？”对于这样的提问，“前几天，我第一次做了剧场公演，因此，每天都有通过客人的投票来改变名次的经验。”我回答了。</div><div><br></div><div>生田绘梨花在日语配音版中由少女鼠角色出演</div><div>汉格游戏在全国东宝系9月28日开始公开！</div><div><br></div><div>【汉格游戏官方网站】</div><div><a href=\"http://www.hungergames.jp/\">http://www.hungergames.jp/</a></div><div><br></div><div><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2012/09/21/hungergames_004.jpg\"><img alt=\"hungergames_004.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2012/09/hungergames_004-thumb-450x298-1925.jpg\" width=\"450\" class=\"mt-image-center\" style=\"text-align: center; display: block; margin: 0 auto 20px;\"></a></div><div><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2012/09/21/hungergames_002.jpg\"><img alt=\"hungergames_002.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2012/09/hungergames_002-thumb-450x298-1927.jpg\" width=\"450\" class=\"mt-image-center\" style=\"text-align: center; display: block; margin: 0 auto 20px;\"></a></div><div><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2012/09/21/hungergames_005.jpg\"><img alt=\"hungergames_005.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2012/09/hungergames_005-thumb-450x298-1929.jpg\" width=\"450\" class=\"mt-image-center\" style=\"text-align: center; display: block; margin: 0 auto 20px;\"></a></div> \t\t</div>","transTitle":"参加了“汉格游戏”的高级试映会。","url":"http://blog.nogizaka46.com/staff/smph/2012/09/007280.php"}